Main Feature Requirements
======================================================
* SSO typo3.org
* Repository creation on request (Rabbit MQ)
* Membership-Requests (Form/Mail)
* Customize Startpage (https://github.com/txinto/redmine_startpage ?)
* Votes on Issues (?)

